01:38:21,982 --> 01:38:25,179
Otherwise you reach a point
where you don't see people,

1761
01:38:25,342 --> 01:38:27,537
you just see books.

1762
01:38:27,702 --> 01:38:30,091
No don't think so much, Antonio.

1763
01:38:31,182 --> 01:38:35,733
What a beautiful couple, magical,
so "genuwine," so sudden.

1764
01:38:35,902 --> 01:38:37,494
My hairs are on end.

1765
01:38:37,662 --> 01:38:41,211
-Thanks for the suit, cousin.
-No problem. You look great.

1766
01:38:41,382 --> 01:38:45,773
