You know what weddings are like.

1767
01:38:45,942 --> 01:38:47,614
Where's Manolito?

1768
01:38:47,782 --> 01:38:50,580
-At home. He's looking great.
-What a funny guy.

1769
01:38:50,742 --> 01:38:51,936
Great party!

1770
01:38:52,102 --> 01:38:55,014
You've got some nerve.
I knew what you were up to.

1771
01:38:55,182 --> 01:38:57,742
You could see right through me!

1772
01:38:59,422 --> 01:39:00,571
-Serafín.
-Yeah?

1773
01:39:00,742 --> 01:39:02,698
-Does it hurt?
-Like hell, but who cares?

1774
01:39:02,862 --> 01:39:04,978
-Have you got a moment?
-Course, shoot.

1775
01:39:05,142 --> 01:39:06,621
No, but in private.

1776
01:39:06,782 --> 01:39:07,931
Sure.

1777
01:39:08,542 --> 01:39:13,821
Well, since I've graduated
I'm at a bit of a loose end.

1778
01:39:14,182 --> 01:39:19,131
I thought, seeing you've got
so many companies,

1779
01:39:19,302 --> 01:39:21,532
