or for you.

1780
01:39:21,702 --> 01:39:24,421
Because I know a lot about law.

1781
01:39:24,582 --> 01:39:26,493
You can trust me, Serafín.

1782
01:39:26,662 --> 01:39:30,860
Well Gonzalo, that's something I've
been thinking about for a while.

1783
01:39:31,222 --> 01:39:34,817
You won't be my lawyer,
you'll be my right-hand man.

1784
01:39:34,982 --> 01:39:38,770
I used to push pills at weekends
in Valencia.

1785
01:39:39,142 --> 01:39:42,214
In Puzzle, Barbacoa, Baraca...

1786
01:39:42,382 --> 01:39:44,338
And now that...

1787
01:39:44,502 --> 01:39:47,858
