in no time. I've even got a lawyer.

1871
01:45:41,022 --> 01:45:43,297
2,000 euros? I don't know...

1872
01:45:43,462 --> 01:45:46,693
I'll probably have to pay out
three times as much.

1873
01:45:47,302 --> 01:45:51,614
But don't thank me.
We'll both make a killing.

1874
01:45:51,782 --> 01:45:56,094
When I get a hunch, the bell rings.
And this'll be one hell of a bell.

1875
01:46:04,342 --> 01:46:05,457
Violeta.

1876
01:46:05,942 --> 01:46:07,216
What's wrong?

1877
01:46:25,262 --> 01:46:26,695
Aren't you going?

1878
01:46:30,142 --> 01:46:34,579
Maybe I rushed into things saying

1879
