1884
01:46:50,862 --> 01:46:52,773
-And not too far away.
-No.

1885
01:46:52,942 --> 01:46:54,091
Up Elipa!

1886
01:46:54,262 --> 01:46:57,698
Come on, Jorge, we've fucking won.
